com.mcc.ul
Class AoConfig

java.lang.Object
  com.mcc.ul.AoConfig

public class AoConfig
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides methods to get or set configuration of an analog output subsystem on a DAQ device. To create an instance of this class, call the getConfig() method of the AoDevice class.
